OL,5, The Post Office chairman has stepped   
OL,6, down amid ongoing tensions around the  
OL,7, Horizon IT scandal that saw hundreds of
OL,8, sub-postmasters wrongly convicted.     
OL,10,FThe organisation said Henry Staunton   
OL,11,Fhad been asked to leave the post by    
OL,12,FBusiness Secretary Kemi Badenoch.      
OL,14,FShe said she felt new leadership was   
OL,15,Fneeded, with the company "rightfully"  
OL,16,Funder heightened scrutiny as the public
OL,17,Foutcry over the scandal continues.     
OL,19,FAn interim chair is expected to be     
OL,20,Fappointed shortly.                     
